          20 4a 07 b2 f2 1c 1a 36 30 e7 df 89 83 ff 36 82 
  aeskey: urtubjtnuihvntcreeeecvbregfjibtn
          ec de 18 db e7 6f bd 0c 33 33 0f 1c 35 48 71 db 
Output:
          87 92 eb fe 26 cc 13 00 a8 c0 00 10 b4 08 6f 5b 

